chief executive officer meyrowitz has been president of tjx since  chief executive officer since january  and a director since  tjx is the leading offprice retailer of apparel and home fashions in the us and worldwide with over  billion in sales and approximately  associates tjx operates tj maxx marshalls homegoods aj wright and bob’s stores in the us winners and homesense in canada and tk maxx in europe previously meyrowitz was president of the marmaxx group the largest division of tjx from  to  she served as senior executive vice president of tjx from  to  and executive vice president from  to  prior she served as executive vice president merchandising for marmaxx she also held senior merchandising and management positions at chadwick’s of boston and hit or miss former divisions of tjx meyrowitz joined tjx in  she is also a director of amscan holdings inc among her philanthropic activities meyrowitz is a member of the board of overseers for the joslin diabetes center about staples staples inc invented the office superstore concept in  and today is the worlds largest office products company with  talented associates the company is committed to making it easy to buy a wide range of office products including supplies technology furniture and business services with  sales of  billion staples serves consumers and businesses ranging from homebased businesses to fortune  companies in  countries throughout north and south america europe and asia headquartered outside of boston staples operates more than  office superstores and also serves its customers through mail order catalog ecommerce and contract businesses more information is available at wwwstaplescom multimedia files download all files downloaddownload thumbnail  kb contact staples incpaul capelliowen davis  search staples news search this site stay informed learn about staples news as its happeningsign up to have press releases emailed directly to you international sites australia brazil canada china see all  int