of tjx however meyrowitz became president on october   additionally she became a member of the board of directors on september   she was appointed chief executive officer of the company on january   replacing acting ceo bernard cammarata the chairman of the board for tjx in january  she was replaced as chief executive officer of tjx by ernie herrman  media recognitionedit she ranked th on cnns  most powerful women in business  in  forbes ranked her th in their list of the  most powerful women as of  she is listed as the th most powerful woman in the world by forbes see alsoedit zayre referencesedit  a b c d e the tjx companies inc names carol meyrowitz president business wire gale group  retrieved    a b the worlds  most powerful women forbes forbes retrieved  june    mpw   fortune fortune retrieved  march    jewish voice new york the world’s most powerful jewish women by jen levey september     to watch carol meyrowitz boston business journal december   retrieved october     a b c d e carol meyrowitz profile forbescom retrieved    meyrowitz moving on herrman moving up at tjx gale group november  retrieved  dead link  the tjx companies inc announces election of carol meyrowitz to chief executive officer marketwatch inc  retrieved    the tjx companies inc announces election of ernie herrman to ceo carol meyrowitz becomes executive chairman yahoo finance retrieved      most powerful women in business  carol meyrowitz cnn moneycom retrieved    the  most powerful women forbescom   external linksedit reuterscompermanent dead link brief biography of carol meyrowitz v t e tjx companies current assets homegoods homesense marshalls tj maxx tk maxx sierra trading post winners former assets ajwright bjs wholesale club bobs stores homebase the maxx stylesense zayre trade secret key people carol meyrowitz retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlecarolmeyrowitzoldid categories american women chief executivesamerican jewsliving peopleamerican retail chief executivesrider un